        "rich_text_qVyerJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Consider Upgrading Your Engagement Ring?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Consider Upgrading Your Engagement Ring?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "why-consider",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_bEtGef": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Why_Consider_Upgrading_Your_Engagement_Ring_a7074c5a-30db-4f44-9cac-0642ebf5fe12.png",
            "text": "<p>There’s rarely one single reason, it's usually a combination of sentiment, style and timing. Some couples start their lives together with a modest ring and now want something closer to their dream design. Others want to celebrate a milestone - an anniversary, a first home, a child or a moment that changed their life. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_G6xFCJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Consider Upgrading Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Sometimes your taste evolves. Maybe you once loved a simple solitaire but now find yourself drawn to halos or modern architectural settings Or you want something that feels a little more exclusive, a little more “you.” And sometimes it’s practical, your current ring might feel too delicate for everyday wear, or you want a stone that feels more significant. Whatever the reason an upgrade isn't about replacing memories. It's about celebrating growth and love.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Popular Ways to Upgrade an Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Popular Ways to Upgrade an Engagement Ring</h2><p>If you’re researching popular engagement rings, you’ll notice that most designs fall into a few categories. These same approaches also guide how couples upgrade their rings today.</p><p>Here are the most effective and meaningful upgrade options.</p>",
            "custom_id": "popular",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Redesign the Setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Redesign the Setting</h3><p>This is the easiest way to refresh your ring while keeping your diamond.</p><ul><li>You can add <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/halo-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Halo\">Halo</a></li><li>Change to bezel</li><li>Rotate your stone to the east west setting</li><li>Switch from <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/wedding-rings-yellow-gold\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"yellow gold\">yellow gold</a> to platinum </li><li>Upgrade the prongs for more security</li></ul><p>These kinds of changes let you design diamond ring details without replacing the stone you cherish.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Redesigning is perfect if you love your original diamond but want a ring that feels more modern</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_8Ew9eG": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Redesign_the_Setting_16_9_8c7acfb1-bfd2-4564-8b7d-f2bd337ec8e0.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Add Accent Stones or a Diamond Band",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Add Accent Stones or a Diamond Band</h3>",
            "custom_id": "carat",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_fPxpk3": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Add_Accent_Stones_or_a_Diamond_Band.png",
            "text": "<p>A subtle upgrade with a big visual impact.</p><p>Side stones like baguettes, trillions, or small rounds create balance and brilliance. Or you can introduce a diamond band, which is one of the most popular ways to elevate engagement rings without altering the main stone. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_zjeiKt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lucira Tip: If you want a noticeable upgrade without altering your diamond, adding a diamond band is often the most elegant option</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6tcaY6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Repurpose Your Original Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Repurpose Your Original Diamond</h3><p>Many couples feel deeply connected to their original stone. Repurposing keeps that emotional value alive</p><ul><li>You can put the diamond into a new setting</li><li>Turn it into a pendant </li><li>Use it for future heirloom </li><li>Or add it into a multi stone design </li></ul><p>It's a way of keeping your story close and refreshing the design.</p><p><strong>Lucira Tip:</strong> turning the original diamond into a pendant is a meaningful way to keep your first chapter with you always.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_nDE6aQ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Repurpose_Your_Original_Diamond.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WCya9q": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choosing Between a New Ring or a Redesign",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Choosing Between a New Ring or a Redesign</h2><p>Some couples look up engagement vs <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/wedding-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"wedding ring\">wedding ring</a> meaning to understand how each piece fits into their story before deciding on an upgrade. Still, the best choice is the one that feels right for your style today.</p><p>A redesign is perfect if you:</p><ul><li>Want to keep your original diamond</li><li>Like the sentimental connection</li><li>Want a refreshed look</li><li>Prefer a cost friendly upgrade </li></ul><p>A new ring is ideal when you:</p><ul><li>Want a new shape or size</li><li>Feel your original design no longer reflects you</li><li>Want to create a new chapter entirely </li></ul><p>Both are meaningful choices, it simply depends on what feels authentic to you</p>",
            "custom_id": "choosing",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_RxrhzB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Full Redesign ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Full Redesign </h3><p>A full redesign gives you complete freedom.</p><p>You can choose:</p><ul><li>A new diamond ring</li><li>A larger carat size</li><li>A different metal </li><li>A modern setting</li><li>Custom details</li></ul><p>This is often chosen by couples browsing design diamond ring ideas or anyone wanting to truly rebuild their ring from the ground up.<br/> <br/>Lucira Tip: Some couples keep the original ring and build a new ring to complement it. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_MLHbYJ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fully_Redesign_16_9_51347869-7ec7-4e04-bca2-0f7eef79d358.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_zQKVxi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Partial Redesign ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Partial Redesign </h3><p> A partial redesign lets you keep your centre diamond but change everything around it.</p><p>You can: </p><ul><li>Change the band</li><li>Add side stones</li><li>Switch metals</li><li>Refine proportions </li></ul><p>It's a middle path, meaningful but not involving a drastic change.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Even adjusting the height of the diamond can transform the overall look and comfort.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_HTQPx9": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Partial_Redesign_16_9.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_w6QFfD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira’s approach to ring upgrades",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lucira’s approach to ring upgrades</h2><p>At Lucira, every upgrade begins with your story.</p><p>We look at what you love about your current ring, what you want to change, and how you envision the next chapter.</p><p>Whether you want something subtle or something completely new our team helps you create a ring that feels aligned with who you are today and the life you’re building ahead</p>",
            "custom_id": "lucira",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UnGMpL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion: A ring that grows with you",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: A ring that grows with you</h2><p>Your engagement ring captured a moment in time, your beginning.</p><p>Upgrading it celebrates everything that has happened since.</p><p>Whether you redesign the setting, add sparkle, choose a new shape, or design something from scratch, your upgraded ring should feel like it belongs to the life you’re living now.</p><p>Your relationship has evolved.</p><p>It’s natural for your ring to evolve with it.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
